---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="About — Roger Wibrew">
  <main class="container">
    <h1>About</h1>
    <p>
      I'm a chemical engineer with <strong>25 years of hands-on process operations experience</strong>,
      now combining that knowledge with <strong>machine learning</strong> and
      <strong>modern software engineering</strong>. The combination matters — ML models are only
      as good as the domain understanding behind them, and I bring both.
    </p>
    <p>
      My background spans process operations across multiple industries. I hold
      an <strong>MS in Computer Science with a specialisation in artificial intelligence</strong>,
      which gives me the tools to bridge engineering fundamentals with data-driven methods.
    </p>
    <p>
      My work connects first-principles modeling — thermodynamics, fluid dynamics, control
      theory — with modern implementation: web applications, real-time simulation, and
      AI-assisted analysis. I focus on <strong>process simulation</strong>,
      <strong>dynamic systems</strong>, and <strong>engineering software</strong> that solves
      operational problems across process industries.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is a growing portfolio of technical writing and working tools that show how
      I approach problems: define the assumptions clearly, build models that can be tested,
      and deliver outputs that people can actually use in the field.
    </p>

    <h2>Work With Me</h2>
    <p>
      I'm always open to interesting conversations — whether that's collaborating on a project,
      exploring an idea, or just talking shop about process engineering and ML.
    </p>
    <a class="work-btn" href="/contact">Get in touch &rarr;</a>
  </main>

  <style>
    .container { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 3rem 1.5rem; }
    h1 { margin: 0 0 1.5rem; }
    p { line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text-secondary); }
    strong { color: var(--text-primary); }
    h2 { margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; }
    .work-btn {
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.65rem 1.35rem;
      border-radius: 8px;
      background: var(--accent);
      color: #0b0d12;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
    }
    .work-btn:hover {
      background: var(--accent-hover);
      color: #0b0d12;
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(201, 126, 58, 0.2);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
